# The admin panel reads env vars from the ROOT .env (one directory up).
# For local dev: no admin/.env needed — just ensure the root .env is populated.
# For Vercel: set these in the Vercel dashboard for the admin project.
#
# Required variables (already in root .env):
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
# VITE_API_URL=
